title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
OB: When attempting to export data in a table inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The export operation in a table inside a grid cell should be successful without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
To reproduce: 
1. Insert a grid.
2. Perform an export operation on a table that is inside a grid cell.
